{"tid":2165010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【內地洪災】遲來的習總！首訪災區稱一直牽掛民眾 「臨時演員」扮村婦迎接","createTime":"2020-08-19T13:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T03:37:34.000Z","uid":36494,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6e03fc7c5ce6d8256cc0d5ecafac5dba01cac568","tid":2165010,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"自6月以來汛情嚴重，中共總書記習近平昨日終於首度前往災區勘災。官媒今天報道，習近平在安徽視察時說，一直牽掛災區的民眾；並稱「中華民族同自然災害鬥了幾千年，積累了寶貴經驗，我們還要繼續鬥下去」。有眼尖的網友揭發，稱<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">官媒公佈習近平勘災的照片中的「災民」，竟然是「臨時演員」，真正身份是安徽阜南縣治安大隊副隊長閆靜。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200819/GFQ4RWNL4ZCPHB5MVF7UIDQE4Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200819%2FGFQ4RWNL4ZCPHB5MVF7UIDQE4Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufXpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=978df225\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200819%2FGFQ4RWNL4ZCPHB5MVF7UIDQE4Q%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=36d7400c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200819/GFQ4RWNL4ZCPHB5MVF7UIDQE4Q/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"48b17970b59f99fd72705f637b56e0d7c62c005c","tid":2165010,"uid":32722,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"北戴河會議俾人圍屌完喇？"},{"pid":"c7db6510fcdfdd051609f096b8e77aec55760986","tid":2165010,"uid":224533,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:59:22.000Z","msg":"視察洪災但地下一滴水都冇"},{"pid":"240331d1bc1755aa457961275798047e1410fc24","tid":2165010,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"有網友指出，每逢中共官方需要類似「宣傳照」時，就會安排各地區的官員與公務員充當「鄉民」。不只這位像極閆靜的婦女被質疑，就連她手中抱的孩子，也一度被網友質疑是臨時演員。另外還有網友批評中共的做法，根本是「自欺欺人」。"},{"pid":"efdc09e781a5e14d26da323c560918ef624422ff","tid":2165010,"uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:00:56.000Z","msg":"網民又同時質疑一張習總在田裏與農民交談、了解防汛救災和災後恢復生產情況的照片，特別是照片中的黑影很「奇特」：「農民和官員的影子，方向不統一的，透視位錯晒；習總與農民腳下都無影；農民們身上都各有不同的『別人暗影』。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4q3cSJg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4q3cSJg.png&h=940bdbd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"234893a0701c22abb6c4f6ee427e47f41a9f6565","tid":2165010,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"霞姨，收返佢個飯盒"},{"pid":"f0e33f61456d3f10c7743d339b5aa9959feff9ed","tid":2165010,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:05:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3162536c6e6d4aa3a5ae5ff1dd1323d44a9fe1e5","tid":2165010,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b5f7726f05d0a6b7a974b0b48372fcab2f7eae34","tid":2165010,"uid":132698,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔係想幫班大劣人<br />\n不過真係唔明點解班人喺水災果陣<br />\n咁想見到維尼落去親身視察民情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢落去又幫到d乜？<br />\n宜家通訊咁方便<br />\n佢要了解災情的話<br />\n睇片隨時都睇到乜都知<br />\n要幫都晨早落指令幫左啦"},{"pid":"1dc65facfd4d76bf3da55731fc300665d6ded872","tid":2165010,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5f7726f05d0a6b7a974b0b48372fcab2f7eae34","tid":2165010,"uid":132698,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T14:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔係想幫班大劣人<br />\n不過真係唔明點解班人喺水災果陣<br />\n咁想見到維尼落去親身視察民情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class